Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}（内衣性交比裸体更让人讨厌 木南日菜)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}明明睡在床上就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那我出门了哦 - 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}会感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}已经交了新男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}也别这样说啊，咱们先进屋\N哈？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}要多少？ - 我没那个意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}若是这样的话 五万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我现在身上没那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}别这样 他在睡觉呢 我现在就去拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我想要的不是钱 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你吻我的话 我就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}说话算数吗？ - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}就这一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}继续啊 这样不能算接吻吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}想让我快点回去对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你可以走了吧 - 舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我才不要伸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 - 来吧\N放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 会吵醒他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你不要出声就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你看这样不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}快住手 - 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}一下就湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不想我停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行...讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要 - 这是什么？ - 住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}兴奋了吧？ - 才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}想被发现吧？ - 没有 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}睡得好熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不会醒的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}好爽 - 很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}会叫出声来的 吻我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}身体转过来 脸朝下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}头躺好 明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行 - 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}为什么这么湿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}因为你做那种事情啊 不要再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}里面全是水 多久没做了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}跟你没关系 不要问那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要再做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}要去了？...因为快去了对吧？\N才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我来让你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你想把他吵醒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}叫醒他也没关系吗？ - 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那把腿张开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}有很爽吗？ - 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}也让我爽一下啊 - 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我已经兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}什么啊？不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我去叫他好了 - 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}过来 - 不能过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我去叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要过去 - 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}看他满脸的幸福啊，呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要... - 脚放上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}边说不要不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}却这么湿的人是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不是的...那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}告诉我是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}会吵醒他的 不要啊...\N所以不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行了... - 很爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}才不会爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}再多做点吧 这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 会吵醒他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}你快去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不会吧 更湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行 - 不爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行 快要忍不住了 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}快...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}来吧来吧 - 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手.要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}想让他醒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那就乖乖给我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}给我口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}要叫他吗？ - 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}那样好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}这样可以了 - 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要 - 继续做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}奶子露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}来 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}乳头硬了 - 不要摸我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要出声 - 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}等等 你是想让我射吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}做爱吧 - 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}会醒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}快住手吧真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}求你了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不行 快喷了 住手 快喷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}来床上让我爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}住手 - 想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}等等..\N一下下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,


